Product is authentic, Delivered in less than 24 hours and in good condition. perfect and very handy gadget for your activities. lazada's order tracking is very efficient. highly recommended.

Thumbs Up! :)
Could be better on some things!

First time buying a GoPro, always wanted to buy one but the no stabilization always turned me off. This one has finally got stabilization but it's far from perfect. You can only use it up to 2.7k and can't use it at 4k. Night shots are still below average with a lot of digital noise when viewed. The touch LCD is a nice addition but for it not to work when even semi wet is a sore point for me (Even waterproof cell phones have touch screens that work even when semi dry but it doesn't). The voice command is awesome if you use it in a quiet environment but most of the places you go to are never that quiet. All in all a much better GoPro than the last version with room for further improvements!
